{/* Project Overview */}

Quantum-Enhanced Drug Discovery

Our project combines quantum computing with deep learning to accelerate breast cancer drug discovery, achieving 40% faster molecular docking simulations than classical methods.

{/* Technology Stack */}

Research Stack

Quantum algorithms (VQE, QAOA), TensorFlow Quantum, PyTorch, RDKit, molecular dynamics simulations, and high-performance computing clusters.

{/* Global Impact */}

Global Research Collaboration

Collaborating with leading cancer research institutes and quantum computing facilities worldwide to accelerate therapeutic discovery.

{/* Scientific Approach */}

Our Quantum Machine Learning Approach

Combining quantum variational algorithms with deep neural networks to predict drug-target interactions with 92% accuracy against HER2-positive breast cancer cells.

{/* Contact */}

Research Inquiries
